                히로시마시에서 시마나미로!당일치기 관광 코스를 소개합니다!              </h2>
              <ul class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3 post-contents__info">
                <li>
                                      <ul class="flex flex-wrap text-sm -mx-2 post-categories">
                      <li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/ko/destination-ko/">Destination</a></li><li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/ko/tips-ko/">Tips</a></li><li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/ko/%eb%b6%84%eb%a5%98%eb%90%98%ec%a7%80-%ec%95%8a%ec%9d%8c/">분류되지 않음</a></li>                    </ul>
